column5: Finally got my afternoon to relax and fish. With the cooler temps today, the larger pannies have started feeding. I was after perch....  ..., but I'll settle for a plate full of 8-9" pannies any day.  Now that I'm sated, it's off to bed. 3am comes too soon.
mmmm........ pannies  I gotta get out and get me some supper!
Someone will be eating well Great job Bruce     Glad you were able to get out!!! Jacques
Nice crop of eattin their good job.   Art
Never mind I thought it said "Panties"
Those just aren't worth the trouble or expense any more
